# Force LF line endings on checkout regardless of platform. Without this,
# Windows runners check out with CRLF (default `core.autocrlf=true`) and
# `oxfmt --check` flags every file because oxfmt's `endOfLine` default is
# `lf`. `text=auto` lets git auto-detect text vs binary so binary blobs
# aren't normalised.
* text=auto eol=lf
